metadata.name: Forever A Hero's Soul #1/10
metadata.description:
“Forever A Hero’s Soul” (2022)  
__________  
Procreate [3200 x 3200]  
A tribute to the White Ranger.

Calla lilies lined in gold symbolize the rebirth and reconstruction of the soul. A Nogitsune shrouded, carrying the weight of his curse, marked with semicolons. A green lit flame for those who know.  
_________  
Rest easy king.. JDF
